    "In the down sample operation, the Max-Pooling (1 9 2) operation is performed first horizontally and then vertically.The process performed up to this step is also a kind of feature extraction process.",
    "Because new features are obtained from the data with kernel filters.",
    "Feature selection must be made based on the obtained features.",
    "At this stage, the Max-Pooling method, which is also preferred and applied in the literature, was used [54,55].",
    "In the Max-Pooling method, the maximum value of the pooling region is selected to prevent the maximum value from being lost."
  ],
